CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 31, 1958, pg. A12 reads: "Slim And Lovely - Christine Sumpter models a fragile Spanish lace cocktail gown in Trendettes' show. It is created with a side slit, a deeply cut back and features a mantilla for her pretty hair-do."
TitMainTitle: Full length portrait of Christine Sumpter wearing light colored satin sleeveless knee length dress with bow on side and floral lace shawl, modeling for Trendettes' fashion show, Carnegie Music Hall
